<topic template="Default" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="../helpproject.xsd">
  <title translate="true">Grid Angle Dialog Box</title>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para style="margin-bottom:10px; line-height:2.0;"><text styleclass="Heading1" translate="true">Grid Angle Dialog Box</text></para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">The </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Grid Angle</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> dialog box is used to change the angle of the grid. It is displayed by selecting </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Grid|Specify Grid Angle…</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> &#160;The user then enters an angle (in degrees) in the edit box and clicks the </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">OK</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> button to change the angle of the grid as viewed from the top. &#160;The grid will be rotated around its center. &#160;The grid angle is measured counterclockwise from the X-axis. &#160;The axis of rotation is always vertical.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">See also: </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="Specifying_a_Grid_with_Numbers" styleclass="Normal" translate="true">Specifying a Grid with Numbers</link><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> and </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="Editing_the_Grid" styleclass="Normal" translate="true">Editing the Grid</link><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
  </body>
</topic>
